title: Briefing by Alexei Ulyukayev following the meeting (Government of the Russian Federation)
text: ( Source : Government of the Russian Federation ) The current annual meeting of the Foreign Investment Advisory Council was preceded by intensive work during the past year. We carried out the relevant instructions made at the last meeting.
